OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry, sunny and chilly start.
OL,6,FCloud bubbling up during the morning
OL,7,Fbut still with sunny intervals. Cloud
OL,8,Fthickening through the afternoon, with
OL,9,Fa chance of isolated showers later.
OL,10,FLight winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloud breaking through the
OL,13,Fevening, with some late sunny spells.
OL,14,FInland showers easing before cloud
OL,15,Fthickens overnight, with coastal
OL,16,Fshowers and light winds continuing.
OL,17,FCold with a chance of frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
