OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FA cold and rather bright
OL,6,Fstart. Becoming increasingly cloudy
OL,7,Fthrough the morning as frequent
OL,8,Fshowers spread west, these perhaps
OL,9,Fheavy in the afternoon. Winds
OL,10,Fremaining light.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FDry
OL,13,Fwith sunny spells on Tuesday. Dry but
OL,14,Fcloudy on Wednesday and Thursday,
OL,15,Fespecially near coasts. Breezy,
OL,16,Fparticularly over hills, feeling cool
OL,17,Fnear coasts. Chilly by night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
